Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.76,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,下次让你吃一下那个果酱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.57,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,不 祐一去吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.66,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,我对果酱过敏
